               <scopecontent id="aspace_9323b0896636b4e31babb24749517d99">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The files include testimonials and surveys written by Yale students and student employers who participated in the Bulldogs in the Bluegrass program, which faciliates summer internships for Yale students in Louisville, Kentucky. Dates for electronic materials were determined by the files' last modified date.</p>
